================================================================================
ATTRIBUTION / NOTICE
================================================================================

rampart-ke is a derivative work built on Rampart by National Design Studio,
used under CC BY 4.0:

    Rampart — https://huggingface.co/nationaldesignstudio/rampart
              https://github.com/nationaldesignstudio/rampart
    © National Design Studio, licensed CC BY 4.0.

Changes made by rampart-ke: adds an on-device deterministic recognizer layer for
Kenyan identifiers (KRA PIN, M-Pesa codes, Kenyan phone numbers, National ID /
Maisha Namba, SHA/SHIF, NHIF, NSSF, bank/passport, company names, and local
geography), localizes the keep-set policy for Kenyan counties, and wraps the
upstream guard with Kenyan-friendly placeholder tokens.

Rampart's model was fine-tuned on the OpenPII 1.5M dataset
(https://huggingface.co/datasets/ai4privacy/pii-masking-openpii-1.5m), also
licensed CC BY 4.0.
